    "description": "Collection tim bug nghiem trong - VoltNexus Reporting Service\n\n## CAC BUG DA PHAT HIEN:\n\n### 1. CRITICAL - Authentication Bypass\n- SecurityConfig.java:26 - anyRequest().permitAll()\n- Admin APIs khong co bao ve\n\n### 2. CRITICAL - Null Pointer Exception\n- AdminBackfillController.java:62,105 - Khong check null getBody()\n\n### 3. CRITICAL - Missing Input Validation\n- ReportingController.java:22 - Khong validate SalesRecordRequest\n\n### 4. MEDIUM - NumberFormatException\n- ReportController.java:160,163,188 - Long.valueOf() co the crash\n\n### 5. MEDIUM - Information Disclosure\n- SalesReportingService.java:157 - Leak exception details\n\n### 6. LOW - Missing Rate Limiting\n- AI Forecast va Sync APIs khong co rate limit",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "51838372",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/51838372-77c4bfe5-e951-4665-9051-93404c1fa624?source=collection_link"
